         MACRO
         COURSES &COLS=45,&WIDTH=3
         GBLA  &COUSPC,&COUWDTH
         GBLC  &COURSES(20)
         LCLA  &INDX,&WORK
&COUSPC  SETA  &COLS
&COUWDTH SETA  &WIDTH
.LOOP    ANOP
&INDX    SETA  &INDX+1
&COURSES(&INDX) SETC '&SYSLIST(&INDX)'
         DC    CL&WIDTH'&COURSES(&INDX)'
         AIF   (&INDX LT N'&SYSLIST).LOOP
&WORK    SETA  &COLS-&INDX*&WIDTH
         DC    CL&WORK' '
         DC    CL4' '
         MEND
